    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で！　こころが提案する\n冬の北海道が盛り上がるアイデアは、こちら！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And so! Here is the idea that Kokoro proposes\nto get winter in Hokkaido fired up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5000001987,
      "endTime": 8.601746090199999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.7950794618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "荘厳な流氷群の上で華麗なダンスパフォーマンス！\n葵さんによる「流氷ツアーのアピール」！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A magnificent dance performance on the majestic drift ice!\nAoi-san will “appeal for the drift ice tour”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7950794618,
      "endTime": 16.592471639499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7791381916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "名物のワカサギ釣りを猛烈アピール！\n愛ちゃんの「ワカサギ1000匹釣るまで帰れま千」！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Vehemently appealing for smelt fishing‚ a local specialty!\nAi-chan’s “I won’t go home until I catch 1000 smelt!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7791381916,
      "endTime": 23.3932422718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5799088241
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "北海道の最先端スイーツを突撃取材！\n莉央さんの「北海道一番人気のパンケーキ屋紹介」！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A surprise visit to Hokkaido’s most cutting-edge sweets!\nRio-san’s “Introducing Hokkaido’s Most Popular Pancake Shop”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5799088241,
      "endTime": 31.1470062971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.3403393825
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……あのね、こころ、アイデアは\nただ出せばいいってものじゃないんだからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You know‚ Kokoro‚ ideas\naren’t just something you blurt out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3403393825,
      "endTime": 36.5521760066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスするだけでアピールになるのかな？\n大体、流氷の上って滑って踊りにくそうだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will just dancing be enough to appeal to people?\nAnd besides‚ it seems like it’d be hard to dance on the ice because it’s slippery.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7521759112,
      "endTime": 44.5021757206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.7088423491
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、それ以前に危ないですから！\nそれに、私の1000匹だって無謀過ぎるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ it’s dangerous!\nAnd my 1000 fish goal is way too reckless!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7088423491,
      "endTime": 51.0399760007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.2533091624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ええ～？　バラエティー的にはすっごく美味しい\n企画だと思ったんだけどな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh? I thought it was a really good idea for a variety show.\nI thought it would be a hit~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2533091624,
      "endTime": 57.62432976549999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.8243296702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "大体、私の担当企画、冬関係ないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ my plan has nothing to do with winter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8243296702,
      "endTime": 61.9949191649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.2015857458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "そちらは北海道の浦河産のいちごを使った\n絶品パンケーキの試食を予定してますぅ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s going to be a tasting of delicious pancakes made with strawberries from Urakawa‚ Hokkaido.\nWe're planning to have a tasting of exquisite pancakes~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.2015857458,
      "endTime": 69.2280938864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.4147607248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "…………\nそれなら、まぁ……アリかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……\nIn that case‚ I guess… it’s okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4147607248,
      "endTime": 74.5627197665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.7760531188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "線引き、だいぶゆるゆるだね……\nまぁ、莉央らしいと言えばらしいか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re pretty lenient…\nWell‚ I guess it’s typical of Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7760531188,
      "endTime": 80.4014725448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.5948057255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
