      "text": "ちなみに、こころは何する予定だったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What were you planning to do‚ Kokoro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.5948057255,
      "endTime": 83.5564611515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "石狩鍋にてっぽう汁などなど\n北海道の冬のグルメリポートです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ishikari nabe‚ teppou-jiru‚ and so on…\nA winter gourmet report on Hokkaido!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7631277324,
      "endTime": 89.1382071734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.3448738974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんを太らせてしまう訳にはいきませんからね\nここは、こころが代表して――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t let everyone get fat‚ you know.\nSo Kokoro will represent everyone and――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3448738974,
      "endTime": 95.093241207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.2132393441
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "食べたいだけじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You just want to eat!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2132393441,
      "endTime": 96.961625298,
