      "text": "……とはいえ\n私達の案もいまいちピンと来なかった訳で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That being said‚\nour ideas weren’t really clicking…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1549586695,
      "endTime": 101.5895163934,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
