      "text": "ど、どうしたんだ……？　ため息なんかついて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What’s wrong…? Why are you sighing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1552794933,
      "endTime": 113.7423089981,
