      "text": "いやぁ……こころは一人で集中した方が\nアイデア出せる派なので、このまま部屋に残って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… Kokoro’s the type who can come up with ideas better\nwhen she’s concentrating alone‚ so I’ll stay in the room…",
