      "text": "――MC中にイベントや名産品を紹介したり\n……イベントにちなんだ振り付けを追加する、とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Like introducing events or local specialties during the MC segment…\n…Or adding choreography that’s inspired by the event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.4065532685,
      "endTime": 273.7904761315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 273.9971429508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_04-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "こころとどっこいどっこいじゃないですか！\nよくそれでこころのアイデアに文句言えましたねっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not so different from Kokoro’s idea!\nHow can you complain about Kokoro’s idea when yours is the same!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.9971429508,
      "endTime": 280.283083884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
