      "text": "そうですね、このままでは埒があきません\nミクちゃんの客観的意見を求めますっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right‚ we’re not getting anywhere like this.\nLet’s ask for Miku-chan’s objective opinion!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.368254153,
      "endTime": 293.0849888484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
