      "text": "大丈夫だよミク。忖度なんて必要ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay‚ Miku. You don’t have to hold back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.1404562951,
      "endTime": 301.7662159444,
      "sfxList": []
